    hours: "1",
    isTrue: true,
    vehicleNumber: "Vehicle A1",
    price: "100",

    brand: "Brand A2",
    driver: "Driver 2",

    routeNumber: "Route 002",
    hours: "2",
    isTrue: false,
    vehicleNumber: "Vehicle A2",

  {
    brand: "Brand A3",
    driver: "Driver 3",
    customer: "Customer 3",
    routeNumber: "Route 003",
    hours: "3",
    isTrue: true,
    vehicleNumber: "Vehicle A3",
    price: "300",
  },
  // ...
  {
    brand: "Brand A37",
    driver: "Driver 37",
    customer: "Customer 37",
    routeNumber: "Route 037",
    hours: "37",
    isTrue: false,
    vehicleNumber: "Vehicle A37",
    price: "3700",
  },
];
